## [index.d.ts](https://github.com/DefinitelyTyped/DefinitelyTyped/tree/master/types/blobshape/index.d.ts)
````ts
interface BlobshapeParameters {
    size?: number;
    growth?: number;
    edges?: number;
    seed?: string | null;
}

declare function blobshape({ size, growth, edges, seed }?: BlobshapeParameters): {
    path: string;
    seedValue: number;
};

export = blobshape;
````
